<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Posts on 难以想象的晴朗</title><link>https://imzhizi.github.io/post/</link><description>Recent content in Posts on 难以想象的晴朗</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>en-us</language><atom:link href="https://imzhizi.github.io/post/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>疫情随想</title><link>https://imzhizi.github.io/1/01/%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E9%9A%8F%E6%83%B3/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://imzhizi.github.io/1/01/%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E9%9A%8F%E6%83%B3/</guid><description>&lt;p>今天和爸爸聊过去的事情时, 因为记错了一件事情, 被骂越学越傻. 我倒也是特别不难受, 不记得就是不记得, 但还是辩解说十几年来发生的变化太大了, 事情跟着赶着一件追着一件, 根本没时间去好好想想过去就要迎接明天.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>